                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/12471.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Lorillard</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Buenos Aires</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-07-11">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 11, 1914</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>In reply to my note, conveying instructions of July 7, Minister for Foreign
                    Affairs replies today as follows: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>In the name of the Vice President, I reciprocate these declarations which
                            are entirely in accord with the sentiments and intentions which have
                            animated the action of Argentina united with those of Brazil and Chile
                            for the good of American fraternity. It will be always a great cause of
                            pleasure to the Argentine Government to have contributed to a pacific
                            solution doubly flattering as it not only united two nations friendly to
                            us but consecrates the ideal of peace and concord as an efficient force
                            in international relations.</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lorillard</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
